Package fi.tamk.yourtrueself.ui

Contains custom Scene2D UI classes and widgets.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AchievementPanel
    Display panel for a single achievement.
    AchievementPopup
    Achievement popup window.
    AchievementWindow
    Modal window that lists all achievements in a scrollable panel.
    ChallengePanel
    Panel containing challenge information and a button to complete it.
    ChallengeTimerPanel
    A panel that shows time remaining until next challenge is given.
    CharacterImage
    Character portrait.
    CharacterMainPanel
    Character information panel for the main screen.
    CharacterSelectPanel
    Character information panel for the selection screen.
    CreditsDisplay
    Simple scrollable text window with game credits.
    LabeledBar
    ProgressBar widget with a visible progress number.
    PrefsDisplay
    Preferences window.
    StatBar
    Progress bar for a stat.
    StatsDisplay
    Panel that shows player stats in rows.
    VolumeSlider
    Custom Slider with better DPI scaling.
    YTSWindow
    Custom Window class that has a Back button in the title bar and if modal, closes by tapping outside the window.
